# ── SVN Review — files kept OUT of the public repository ─────────────────

# Per-install state: machine-/customer-specific runtime data
# (SVN credentials, registered project paths, review state, caches, sessions).
# The app ships with an EMPTY data/ and recreates it on first run.
data/*
!data/.htaccess
!data/config.json.example

# Build output
dist/

# Local Claude Code tooling (settings, project-specific skills)
.claude/

# Internal working notes — not part of the public distribution
CLAUDE.md
CLAUDE-todo.md
NAMES.md

# Editor / OS noise
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
